data.title: Dumpstaphunk Spotlights Emerging Artists Karina Rykman and R.L. Cooper for Benefit Concert
data.meta_description: Karina Rykman, a bassist and singer-songwriter from New York, and R.L. Cooper, a Mississippi musician based in Miami, share the stage with New Orleans funk outfit Dumpstaphunk.
